ime":"2017-04-22T03:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚晒電騙丫佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加個話字同個案字好難為佢咩？</blockquote><br />\n而家經常都係咁 想屌好耐 學哂大陸啲野<br />\n睇落去又1999"},{"pid":"03af50b8242de8e074817debf9ec4d55d49ce6a7","tid":211380,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑, 只有心中有鬼既人先會中招<br />\n<br />\n正常人頭也不回一野吸佢線啦, 點會比佢呃到"},{"pid":"b4fdf81a2bc5b80b568059540799949799aca5a3","tid":211380,"uid":70864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"每次睇到呢d支畜&quot;精英&quot;中自己同胞伏<br />\n都感到精神為之一振<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15246601fffb88120d976978567099bfd6d73f35","tid":211380,"uid":47819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚晒電騙丫佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加個話字同個案字好難為佢咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想屌好耐<br />\n好支那味既用詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2db7a65bdac925d2189a08f839110fc4be90533","tid":211380,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224a843ea5c74631bf14113b393e22d2bdc4dbbb","tid":211380,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:27:21.000Z","msg":"支那愽士生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3fb59df114bcfc7bbcbe4dc41229500d31c017d","tid":211380,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"還有党<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1143112f17cf307a5e435e84f8efc02b0f1fc9","tid":211380,"uid":51753,"like